Currently  HDB BTO buyers enjoy subsidised prices and CPF Enhanced Housing Grants or EHG (if eligible). For the new Prime Location Public Housing flats in prime areas  prices will be furtherreduced with additional subsidies from the Government.It is not announced how much the additional subsidies will be  but it will likely be fixed for each project (i.e.  unlike the EHG  it will not consider your income).
Extra grants are already ‚Äúfactored‚Äù into the price  will only know when the project is launch. E.g. River peaks at 6%. Actual amount of grant is not known.
